# ExESS -- Changelog

## v1.0.0 (Feb. ??, 2024) - Current

- initial copy of the repository from private GitLab to public GitHub
  + repository structure update >> new folders under `src`
  + reworking of `README.md` to fit the new structure
- changing of distribution integration (**breaking change**)
  + reduction to `Base.rand` for sampling, `cdf`, and `pdf`
  + every distribution gets its own type, for example `MBAzimuthDistribution` for the
    distribution of the azimuth angle of the three-dimensional Maxwell-Boltzmann velocity
    distribution